{"sn1.26:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 1.26 ","sn1.26:0.2":"3. Sattivagga ","sn1.26:0.3":"Pajjotasutta ","sn1.26:1.1":"“Kati lokasmim pajjota, ","sn1.26:1.2":"Tehi loko pakasati; ","sn1.26:1.3":"Bhagavantam putthumagamma, ","sn1.26:1.4":"Katham janemu tam mayan”ti. ","sn1.26:2.1":"“Cattaro loke pajjota, ","sn1.26:2.2":"pancamettha na vijjati; ","sn1.26:2.3":"Diva tapati adicco, ","sn1.26:2.4":"rattimabhati candima. ","sn1.26:3.1":"Atha aggi divarattim, ","sn1.26:3.2":"tattha tattha pakasati; ","sn1.26:3.3":"Sambuddho tapatam settho, ","sn1.26:3.4":"esa abha anuttara”ti. "}